reviewText: This movie pits two antagonists against eachother on a hostile, desert, otherworldly landscape. A chess game between black and white. Famous surprise ending.  Enjoy!
This was a really cool, gritty indie sci fi movie.  It was touching to watch after Ernest Borgnine passed away recently.  He is a great actor, and this was one of his last performances at age 93!
This may be one of the worst movies ever made. The acting is awful,the plot is stupid and the overall quality is just bad. Don't waste your money on this one.
